      <accessrestrict id="aspace_b64653dfebe8aca07f7e679069b131fd">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>This collection is open for research.</p>
         <p>Per curator, permissions for the oral history recordings were granted, however, scanned materials and videos should not be processed until permissions are granted.</p>
         <p>Box 1 (born digital): Restricted fragile. Access copies of digital files may be requested. Consult Access Services for further information.</p>
